quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,37,"Then Adam received from his Lord [some] words,{1} and He accepted his repentance. Indeed, it is He who is the Accepting of Repentance,{2} the Merciful.",footnotes:1:[Allāh taught Adam words of repentance],footnotes:2:[that would be acceptable to Him.]
  2,38,"We said, "
  2,39,"And those who disbelieve and deny Our signs - those will be companions of the Fire; they will abide therein eternally."
